column2: "Welcome back, Master. I am sincerely grateful to you for granting my wish."
"Watching the way you battled, I came to understand a new, deeper level to how an Etoile can fight."
"I expected no less of you, Master. You have my highest esteem! No, my adoration!"
"I wish I could observe you even more closely, but... Ah, I have an idea!"
"If you ever want my help, do not hesitate to call me! I would love to be useful to you as your maid!"
